From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Webkitium Build <build@webkitium.local>
Date: Mon, 20 Apr 2026 01:50:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Windows: Suppress -Wmissing-format-attribute in bmalloc
 Logging.cpp

The BATTRIBUTE_PRINTF macro is correctly applied to the function
declaration, but clang-cl on Windows still emits -Wmissing-format-attribute
warnings for the vfprintf call. Suppress this warning to fix the build.

---
 Source/bmalloc/bmalloc/Logging.cpp | 7 +++++++
 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+)

diff --git a/Source/bmalloc/bmalloc/Logging.cpp b/Source/bmalloc/bmalloc/Logging.cpp
index 1234567..abcdefg 100644
--- a/Source/bmalloc/bmalloc/Logging.cpp
+++ b/Source/bmalloc/bmalloc/Logging.cpp
@@ -26,6 +26,13 @@
 #include "Logging.h"
 #include "BPlatform.h"
 
+// Webkitium: Suppress -Wmissing-format-attribute on Windows/clang-cl.
+// The BATTRIBUTE_PRINTF macro is correctly defined but clang-cl still warns
+// about vfprintf calls with format strings passed from function parameters.
+#if defined(__clang__) && defined(_WIN32)
+#pragma clang diagnostic ignored "-Wmissing-format-attribute"
+#endif
+
 #if !BUSE(OS_LOG)
 #include <stdarg.h>
 #include <stdio.h>
